## Scenario A:
#### A company trains employees on customer service etiquette to improve communication.

<details style="background-color: #ececec; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 145px; width: 45%; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 5px;">
    <summary style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"><b>🔎</b> Answer</summary>
    <div style="margin-top: 10px; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px;">
        <p style="font-size: 14pt;">
            <b>Not Cybersecurity-</b> <i>This scenario is about improving communication skills, not protecting systems, networks, or data from cyber threats.</i>
        </p>
    </div>
</details>

<div style="clear:both;"></div>
